{"tid":265690,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"寫字_迎友","createTime":"2017-05-31T23:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T12:31:31.000Z","uid":120334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2aff68624acb50fecd6faab3950f9832bcaa0ce7","tid":265690,"uid":120334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:38:06.000Z","msg":"先申明我手字未必靚。如果你想試下我幫你寫，可以留言打你要寫啲乜。因為平時都多功課、校務要處理，可能會比較遲應機。歡迎各字友，交流寫字心得。我主要系寫毛筆字，但依家多左用科毛，因為少左系屋企，科毛容易帶就用多左佢。始終毛筆字都要用真毛筆寫。寫字衹系爲了興趣，我並非專業人士。好啦，都叫做第一次系呢度開post，希望有人回下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7360c21b3f2ef948d53abc164b27c27bfa42bf87","tid":265690,"uid":120334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T00:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tkau54bw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftkau54bw&h=4c18a555&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"266be69c3a732aeb785c8860f506c09365d6fb6c","tid":265690,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T00:35:36.000Z","msg":"活動台冇人，開去創意台<br />\n<br />\n仲有打5P字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「系」？？？"},{"pid":"d4eb682714bebd67ce4a33d93adfe3fcfb565861","tid":265690,"uid":120334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>活動台冇人，開去創意台<br />\n<br />\n仲有打5P字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「系」？？？</blockquote><br />\n係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我試下。多謝巴打。"},{"pid":"460617fe7b34eb94146be4bc02c27c58955162fa","tid":265690,"uid":50969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"我逃進洶湧人潮<br />\n尋找藏身的一角"},{"pid":"fa861cb0d8f1dff60a1e32ebab0131aa3f3c8bd0","tid":265690,"uid":120334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我逃進洶湧人潮<br />\n尋找藏身的一角</blockquote><br />\n<